frontmatter.title: Experience: Week One
frontmatter.description: My expeience of week one working on GSoC project with mlpack. There was soo much of discussion with my mentor regarding the goals of the project and what really the project means.

frontmatter.title: Community Bonding
frontmatter.description: A post about mlpack community and how open source impact me as a developer and as a person. You interact with a lot of people and that too amazing people. Looking forward to this amazing journey

frontmatter.title: Hooray!!! GSoC 2021 @ Mlpack
frontmatter.description: I was soo happy when I got the mail that this year I will work with Mlpack as my GSoC project. This is my first time getting accepted at GSoC and feels awesome to be with mlpack.
